            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "Will live in happiness and contentment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "But as of him whose scales are light"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "He will be embraced by an Abyss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "Ah, what will convey to you what that is"
